{"tid":274264,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府修例禁向18歲以下人士售酒精類飲品","createTime":"2017-06-07T07:57:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-08T03:59:40.000Z","uid":20933,"like":137,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a2ef6f6345e17f23a42ee660d7e909b3e7926ada","tid":274264,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T07:57:34.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】政府計劃修例禁止出售酒精類飲品予18歲以下人士，相關條例草案星期五刊憲。<br />\n<br />\n政府計劃於本月21日將條例草案提交立法會審議。條例草案建議禁止售賣和供應酒精類飲品予18歲以下人士，賣方亦有權查閱買酒人士的身分證明文件，同時規定賣酒地方要貼出告示，表明不會向未成年人士賣酒，衞生署將會負責執法。<br />\n<br />\n條例草案建議向未成年人士賣酒可被罰款五萬元，賣酒地方未有貼出告示則可被罰款二萬五千元。"},{"pid":"5acff6760ffa3b3f687c5b3d2a80ed3613ed17ff","tid":274264,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T07:57:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=223918\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D223918&d=lWdkQpLmCgxSW1DATsQyGTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=3eb01c7a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D223918&h=27ab5ede\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=223918</a>"},{"pid":"a0e7bd3d78ab162924b97606fd889537d333765f","tid":274264,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T08:01:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5b24cbbe94c7da5647c5b88d05d330768881366","tid":274264,"uid":98386,"like":3,"dislike":31,"score":-28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T08:01:51.000Z","msg":"垃圾正苦 應做唔做唔應做就做曬"},{"pid":"43d736ecbb96025ab358961dd574a3b198f47e48","tid":274264,"uid":77143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T08:02:35.000Z","msg":"留名睇小學雞比腐皮"},{"pid":"7c170f87fc8f2c5ddf11c77a7366e97551d279fe","tid":274264,"uid":1082,"like":90,"dislike":1,"score":89,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T08:03:11.000Z","msg":"我而家