g src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nJolly Shandy</blockquote><br />\n哦，原來果啲都計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咁班小學雞以後無得係班同學面前威威喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7efe07a1ece961563829f01116697226152cd61","tid":274264,"uid":726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T08:08:33.000Z","msg":"以為不嬲都唔比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5d3919d2dd583b1e062dffceb92396d0ea0291d","tid":274264,"uid":43967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T08:08:44.000Z","msg":"美國有好多州21歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90ee648b063f4abff6c297472a09ef1a8f00ea14","tid":274264,"uid":28619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T08:10:58.000Z","msg":"唔係不嬲唔比架咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ccb44fcf713e89dff6f94fcff688a319bd8fa75","tid":274264,"uid":340,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T08:13:45.000Z","msg":"未夠18歲唔過1%酒精咪買得囉,依家要禁埋佢"},{"pid":"76425f634edfb3f9cbfe6527270460b4d788313c","tid":274264,"uid":31752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T08:14:08.000Z","msg":"酒吧及領酒牌的食肆不准售酒予18歲以下人士，但便利店、超市等零售店舖則不受法例限制，只靠業界遵守實務守則，「學生哥」偷雞買酒飲的情況普遍。食物及衞生局計劃收緊限制，修訂《應課稅品條例》(第109章)及相關附屬法例，禁止任何商業活動中售賣及供應酒精飲品予18歲以下人士，料最快本年度向立法會提交立法建議，由衞生署執行。提供戒酒服務的機構歡迎建議，認為單靠零售業界自我規管，無法杜絕問題。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港是極少數並無在零售點設售酒年齡限制的先進地區，由2000年起，法例109章B《應課稅品(酒類)規例》實施酒牌制度，禁止持酒牌的食店或酒吧在「處所內」，提供可令人醺醉的酒類飲品予18歲以下人士。但青少年在「處所外」飲酒不受法例規限；零售店舖包括便利店及超級市場賣酒予18歲以下人士並不受規管。香港零售管理協會實施同業守則，以自我規管方式限制店舖售酒予未成年人士。但守則落實情況參差，不少學生成功「偷雞」買酒飲。"},{"pid":"6747f448838062a99f88788ff8d7d34669bcecf3","tid":274264,"uid":10340,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T08:15:04.000Z","msg":"冇知一問，18歲以下可以買酒咩？定係要修例連jolly shandy,酒心朱古力都唔俾賣？"},{"pid":"39bbe79d06784cc0ef442028333a06f31b10ef78","tid":274264,"uid":53105,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T08:15:12.000Z","msg":"睇留言就知大家咩年齡層<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 以前好多小朋友幫老豆出街買啤酒，小朋友就買零食"},{"pid":"a7200c843dfd11a1b9f2387f1643725a3544fa2f","tid":274264,"uid":31752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T08:15:31.000Z","msg":"原來一直都係超市7仔自己唔賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d60ab28358e44a801d727a04a96a280b711e1521","tid":274264,"uid":21917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T08:16:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇留言就知大家咩年齡層<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 以前好多小朋友幫老豆出街買啤酒，小朋友就買零食</blockquote><br />\n中學試過幫買老母上PK買  個收銀真係會問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66563a4113bc80cb4d5d9d906762c028f5b6c00a","tid":274264,"uid":22566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T08:17:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇留言就知大家咩年齡層<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 以前好多小朋友幫老豆出街買啤酒，小朋友就買零食</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f80eb8c3fd126f32d5c206154f9d948c0975c19b","tid":274264,"uid":1082,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T08:18:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇留言就知大家咩年齡層<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 以前好多小朋友幫老豆出街買啤酒，小朋友就買零食</blockquote><br />\n我有買過，但我一路以為係佢偷雞賣比我，佢第一次唔賣比我嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class