我一路以為係佢偷雞賣比我，佢第一次唔賣比我嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n以前著校服幫老豆買啤酒冇嘢 仲以為係個士多老細懶得捉 原來根本冇犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我果陣幫我老母買支玉冰燒用黎炒菜咋，條撚樣都唔賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好噉啦<br />\n一陣你會俾上面啲人話你未成年㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89fa9da7ed98576d43a72b68d448cc331ce3bf98","tid":274264,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T10:09:09.000Z","msg":"咁大反應嗰啲一定毛都未出齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04d847d2c2b97ce41b491e037e6c8e0ebc231390","tid":274264,"uid":4000,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T10:19:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我而家先知，18以下可以買酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"251cc2d4b5109b7074df12a7f5f740f43e1df414","tid":274264,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T10:20:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我而家先知，18以下可以買酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但有d店舖無有自己規則唔賣俾你。<br />\n你都吹佢唔漲"},{"pid":"85b8af9f9eb59b7d4f480daa8836740e5956de48","tid":274264,"uid":5151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T10:23:28.000Z","msg":"16歲都買到煙啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4194f569dbfec816ea21a41f51f07d2edf94c84e","tid":274264,"uid":29938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T10:23:31.000Z","msg":"零售不嬲唔犯法<br />\n但有業務守則<br />\n行內有共識唔會賣酒畀18歲以下<br />\n雖然冇法律約束力<br />\n<br />\n不過餐廳提供酒精畀18歲以下就係犯法<br />\n而家係將零售同餐廳睇齊"},{"pid":"3a62370d5da6840cc199cc5526d2e95cc6088123","tid":274264,"uid":121580,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T10:27:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>本身酒牌係規定唔可以俾十八歲以下人士喺鋪頭內飲酒，所以本身買酒係冇問題，好似係</blockquote><br />\n唔關事係7仔無酒牌,但可以賣酒條件係唔可以舖內飲。"},{"pid":"d9b73d6f09ee5dd387a52b27785d3a3529b301f4","tid":274264,"uid":39016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T10:29:52.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 細個去買孖蒸佢都唔賣比我"},{"pid":"f1f29c188add4423fe43ec971fd1e832556d7e83","tid":274264,"uid":65449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T10:30:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>零售不嬲唔犯法<br />\n但有業務守則<br />\n行內有共識唔會賣酒畀18歲以下<br />\n雖然冇法律約束力<br />\n<br />\n不過餐廳提供酒精畀18歲以下就係犯法<br />\n而家係將零售同餐廳睇齊</blockquote><br />\n有錢賺理得你 除非你個樣太細路 否則冇乜見過人會理 做過ok幾個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}